snippet.title: Queer & Chill
snippet.description:
Queer & Chill is a 2D pixel art puzzle game with lots of diversity, a bit of cleverness and a pinch of spiciness!

We're now on Steam! Add us to your whishlists!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1587800/Queer_and_Chill/
